      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1384-1452",
      "markText": "宋仁宗倒是看得开，他回答说：“你知道吗，正是因为我宫中如此冷落，外面人民才会如此快乐。我宫中若像外面如此快乐，那么民间就会冷冷落落也。”",
      "totalCount": 444,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38119173&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1384&rangeEnd=1452",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87a326a07245a70587a7571?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1384&rangeEnd=1452"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38119173_10_7681-7717",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "7681-7717",
      "markText": "一个社会不能没有道德，但道德如果凌驾于一切之上，社会就会陷入空谈的境地。",
      "totalCount": 414,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38119173&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7681&rangeEnd=7717",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87a326a07245a70587a7571?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7681&rangeEnd=7717"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38119173_17_6770-6797",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "6770-6797",
      "markText": "静不是不动，而是不妄动；无欲不是不要欲，而是不要妄欲。",
      "totalCount": 345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38119173&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=6770&rangeEnd=6797",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87a326a07245a70587a7571?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=6770&rangeEnd=6797"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38119173_23_11326-11346",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "11326-11346",
      "markText": "从来都是人，而不仅仅是事实，在构建历史。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38119173&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=11326&rangeEnd=11346",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87a326a07245a70587a7571?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=11326&rangeEnd=11346"
